{
    "chapter": 19,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "19:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>｛卡弗，哈，雅，阿因，撒德。｝此类经文已在《黄牛》章首论述过了。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "19:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这是叙述你的主对他的仆人宰凯里雅的慈恩，我把他的故事讲述给你，以便人们从中吸取教训。</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "19:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当时，他低声祈祷真主，急切地期盼主的应答。</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "19:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他说：“我的主啊，我确已年老体衰，白发苍苍。但我并不对祈祷你感到绝望。每当我祈祷时，你总是会应答我。</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "19:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我担心我死后堂兄弟们因忙于俗务而不能履行宗教职责，而我的妻子又是不能生育的，求你赏赐我一个儿子做我的助手吧。</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "19:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>让他来继承我的圣品，并继承叶尔孤白的部分后裔。主啊！求你使他在宗教、道德和知识方面都成为令人满意的。”</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "19:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主应答了他的祈祷。主呼唤他说：“我要告诉你一个好消息，我已应答了你的祈祷，我将赏赐你一个儿子，他的名字叫叶哈雅——在他之前，我没有给任何人使用过这个名字。”</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "19:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>宰凯里雅对真主的大能感到惊奇，他说：“我怎么会有儿子呢？我的妻子不能生育，而我已老态龙钟了！”</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "19:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>天使说：“如你所说，你的妻子不能生育，你已老态龙钟，但是你的主说，这对真主是容易的。宰凯里雅啊！你以前不存在，但我创造了你。”</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "19:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>宰凯里雅说：“主啊！求你为我设一个征兆吧，好让我安心，以证明这个喜讯必定实现。”真主说：“你的征兆是无缘无故三天不得与人说话。”</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "19:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>宰凯里雅从圣所里走出来见他的族人，他向他们示意说：“你们当朝夕赞颂真主。”</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "19:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他被赐予了叶哈雅。当他到了会说话的年龄，我对他说：“叶哈雅啊！你当尽力坚持《讨拉特》。”他在童年时我就赏赐了他智慧、知识、勤奋和决心。</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "19:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我以来自我的慈恩怜悯他，我使他纯洁无罪。他是一个敬畏主的人，他恪守真主的命令，远离真主的禁令。</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "19:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他孝敬双亲，善待他们。对于服从真主和父母，他不骄傲自大，也不忤逆真主和双亲。</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "19:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他在出生日、死亡日和复活日都会得到来自真主的平安。这是人所经历的最孤独的三个时刻，若能获得平安，将会无惧无忧。</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "19:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当在降示给你的《古兰经》中讲述麦尔彦的故事。当时，她离开家人，独自前往东部的一个地方。</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "19:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>她用一个帷幕遮蔽自己，以免族人在她敬拜真主时看见她。我派吉卜利里天使来到她身边。天使为她显现为一个身材匀称的人，她担心他对她行不轨。</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "19:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当她看到一个身材匀称的人向她走来时，她说：“我祈求至仁主，使我免遭你的侵犯。如果你是敬畏的，害怕主的人。”</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "19:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>吉卜利里说：“我不是凡人，我是你的主派遣的使者，以便赐你一个纯洁善良的儿子。”</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "19:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>麦尔彦惊奇地说：“我怎么会有儿子呢？我丈夫或任何人都没有接触过我，我也不是失节的。”</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "19:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>吉卜利里对她说：“如你所述，任何人都没有接触过你，你也不是失节的。但你的主说，‘无父生子对我是容易的。’被赐予你的儿子将成为世人的迹象，来证明真主的大能，并作为对你和信道者的慈恩。这是真主的判决，是记录在被保护的天牌上的。”</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "19:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>于是，在天仙吹了一口气之后她就怀了孕。她躲避到了一个远离人群的地方。</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "19:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>阵痛迫使她来到一颗椰枣树下。麦尔彦说：“但愿我此前已死，被人遗忘，不至于遭此痛苦。”</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "19:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>尔萨在她脚下呼喊她：“不要忧愁，你的主已在你的下面造化了一条溪水，你可以饮用。</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "19:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你抓住椰枣树，摇晃它，就会得到新鲜的椰枣。”</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "19:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你吃新鲜的椰枣吧，你喝水吧，你以自己的孩子而高兴吧，你不要忧愁。如果遇到有人问你，你就说：“我已向我的主发愿，不与任何人说话。”</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "19:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>麦尔彦带着自己的孩子来见族人，族人谴责她说：“麦尔彦啊！你确已做了一件严重的事，因为你带来了一个无父的孩子。”</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "19:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>哈伦的妹妹（哈伦是一个清廉的人）“啊！你的父亲不是缺德的，你的母亲也不是失节的。你出自一个高贵纯洁的家族，怎么能带来一个无父的孩子呢？”</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "19:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>她指了指摇篮中的尔萨。她的族人谴责说：“我们怎能与摇篮中的婴儿说话呢？”</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "19:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>尔萨说：“我是真主的仆人，祂赐予我《引支勒》，并使我成为一名先知。</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "19:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他使我无论在哪里都是一名对仆人有益之人，祂命令我只要活着就要履行拜功，交纳天课。</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "19:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂使我孝敬我的母亲，没有使我成为骄傲自大的、违抗祂的人。</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "19:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在我出生、死亡和复活的日子，祂使我免遭恶魔及其帮凶的伤害。在这三个艰难的时刻，恶魔都不会伤害我。”</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "19:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这就是尔萨·本·麦尔彦，这是有关他的真实的言辞，而不是那些对他怀疑和分歧的迷误者的谰言。</p>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "19:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主不会收养儿子，祂绝不会这样做。当祂意欲一件事时，祂只对那件事说：“有”，它就有了。这样的主，是绝不会有子嗣的。</p>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "19:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>清高的真主是我的主，也是你们所有人的主。你们当虔诚地敬拜祂。我对你们所说的，是能够获得真主喜悦的正道。</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "19:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人们对尔萨的事众说纷纭。他的族人分裂成许多派。一部分人信仰他，说他是使者；另一部分人否认他，如犹太教徒。有一些人走向了极端，他们说：“他就是真主。”甚至还有人说：“他是主的儿子。”真主超越于这一切。分歧者真可悲，他们将遭遇复活日的清算和惩罚。</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "19:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那一日，他们的耳真聪，他们的目真明。但这一切无济于事。但是，在今世生活中的不义者的确明显地迷失了正道。他们不为后世而准备，直到他们处于不义的状态时后世突然来临。</p>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "19:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当以悔恨之日警告世人。那时犯罪者将懊悔自己的罪恶，行善者将懊悔自己的善功太少。那时仆人的功过簿将被收起，将受到清算，每个人将得到自己行为的回报。他们被今世生活所欺骗，疏忽了后世，他们不信仰复活日。</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "19:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>万物毁灭后，我将继续存在，我要继承大地，继承大地上的一切。我要任意处置他们，在复活日，他们必将回归于我，接受清算和报应。</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "19:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当铭记，在降示你的《古兰经》中有易卜拉欣的消息，他本是一个诚实的人，他确信真主的迹象，他是真主派遣的先知。</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "19:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当时，他对自己的父亲阿宰尔说：“我的父亲啊！你为何舍真主而崇拜那既不能听又不能看、而且不能为你招福避祸的偶像呢？</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "19:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我的父亲啊！我已通过启示知道了你所不知道的，你追随我吧，我将指引你走正道。</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "19:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我的父亲啊！你不要崇拜和服从恶魔，恶魔是违抗至仁主的，当时，真主命令他为阿丹叩头，他拒绝了。</p>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "19:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我的父亲啊！我担心，如果你在悖信的情况下死去，会遭受至仁主的惩罚，你就会成为恶魔的朋友，与他一起受刑。”</p>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "19:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>阿宰尔对儿子易卜拉欣说：“难道你厌恶我所崇拜的偶像吗？如果你不停止辱骂我的偶像，我一定要用石击你。你应当长时间远离我，不要与我说话，不要与我在一起。”</p>"
        },
        "47": {
            "verses": {
                "19:47": {
                    "id": 47
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>易卜拉欣对父亲说：“祝你平安。你讨厌的事情不会发生。我将为你向我的主祈求饶恕和引导。他对我确是至慈的。</p>"
        },
        "48": {
            "verses": {
                "19:48": {
                    "id": 48
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我将远离你们和你们舍真主而崇拜的偶像。我祈求我的主，我不以任何物举伴他。或许，我不会由于祈祷而变成薄福的人。”</p>"
        },
        "49": {
            "verses": {
                "19:49": {
                    "id": 49
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当他离开他们和他们舍真主而崇拜的偶像时，我为他补偿了背井离乡之痛——赏赐他伊斯哈格，并赐予他叶尔孤白，我使他们都成为先知。</p>"
        },
        "50": {
            "verses": {
                "19:50": {
                    "id": 50
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我把我的慈恩和圣品赏赐给他们，使他们永远享受人们的赞誉。</p>"
        },
        "51": {
            "verses": {
                "19:51": {
                    "id": 51
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当在降示给你的《古兰经》中提及穆萨，他是被选拔的人，他是使者，也是先知。</p>"
        },
        "52": {
            "verses": {
                "19:52": {
                    "id": 52
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我从穆萨右边的山那里召唤他，让他前来密谈，让他听到了真主的话。</p>"
        },
        "53": {
            "verses": {
                "19:53": {
                    "id": 53
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>出于慈恩，我让他的哥哥哈伦成为先知，以响应他的祈求。</p>"
        },
        "54": {
            "verses": {
                "19:54": {
                    "id": 54
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当铭记，在降示给你的《古兰经》中有伊斯玛仪的消息。他是承诺的，言出必行的，他是使者，也是先知。</p>"
        },
        "55": {
            "verses": {
                "19:55": {
                    "id": 55
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他命令他的家人礼拜，交纳天课，他在他的主那里是受喜的。</p>"
        },
        "56": {
            "verses": {
                "19:56": {
                    "id": 56
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当铭记，在降示给你的《古兰经》中有伊德里斯的消息，他是诚实的人，他确信真主的迹象，他是一位先知。</p>"
        },
        "57": {
            "verses": {
                "19:57": {
                    "id": 57
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我提高了他的声望，赐予他圣品，他是有地位的。</p>"
        },
        "58": {
            "verses": {
                "19:58": {
                    "id": 58
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>本章中所提到的先知——从宰凯里雅开始到伊德里斯——都是真主赐予其圣品的阿丹的后裔，也是我使他们与努哈同舟共济者的后裔，也是易卜拉欣和叶尔孤白的后裔。他们属于我所引导并选拔的人，我使他们成为先知。当他们听到真主的迹象时，他们由于畏惧真主而哭泣着向主叩拜。</p>"
        },
        "59": {
            "verses": {
                "19:59": {
                    "id": 59
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在这些被选拔的先知之后出现了一些作恶、迷误的追随者，他们放弃拜功，不按照要求履行拜功，他们顺从私欲，放荡淫乱，他们将在火狱中遭到恶报。</p>"
        },
        "60": {
            "verses": {
                "19:60": {
                    "id": 60
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>除了对自己的过失进行忏悔，并确信真主、力行善功的人。这等人将进入天堂，他们的工作的报酬丝毫也不会减少。</p>"
        },
        "61": {
            "verses": {
                "19:61": {
                    "id": 61
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那是常住的乐园，是至仁主为其善仆预备的。他们未见而归信，真主对他们承诺的天堂－即使是幽玄－必定会来临。</p>"
        },
        "62": {
            "verses": {
                "19:62": {
                    "id": 62
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们在乐园中听不到闲谈和恶语，只听到互相祝安，天使也在向他们祝安。他们所喜欢的食物朝夕被端上来。</p>"
        },
        "63": {
            "verses": {
                "19:63": {
                    "id": 63
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这就是我让那些服从命令，远离禁令的仆人继承的乐园。</p>"
        },
        "64": {
            "verses": {
                "19:64": {
                    "id": 64
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>吉卜利里啊！你告诉穆罕默德（愿主福安之）：“众天使不会擅自降临，他们只奉真主之名而降临。我们将要面对的后世和我们已逝去的今世及其间的一切都属于真主。使者啊！你的主不遗忘任何事。”</p>"
        },
        "65": {
            "verses": {
                "19:65": {
                    "id": 65
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂是天地的创造者，掌管者和设计者。祂创造了天地间的一切，并对其进行管理和安排。故你当只崇拜祂，祂是应受崇拜的，你当坚持崇拜祂。在崇拜方面，祂没有任何匹敌。</p>"
        },
        "66": {
            "verses": {
                "19:66": {
                    "id": 66
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>否认复活的不信道者嘲讽说：“难道当我死去时，要从坟墓中被复活吗？这的确太遥远了。”</p>"
        },
        "67": {
            "verses": {
                "19:67": {
                    "id": 67
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道这个否认复活的人不记得我曾从无中创造了他吗？真主用第一次创造证明复活，尽管复活是更容易的。</p>"
        },
        "68": {
            "verses": {
                "19:68": {
                    "id": 68
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！以你的主发誓，我必定使他们和误导他们的恶魔从坟墓中复活，来到集合之地，然后，我必将他们卑贱地驱赶到火狱的门口，让他们跪在那里。</p>"
        },
        "69": {
            "verses": {
                "19:69": {
                    "id": 69
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>然后，我必从每一迷误的宗派中提出最悖逆的人，即他们的领袖。</p>"
        },
        "70": {
            "verses": {
                "19:70": {
                    "id": 70
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>然后，我知道谁最应该进入火狱遭受火刑。</p>"
        },
        "71": {
            "verses": {
                "19:71": {
                    "id": 71
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人们啊！你们中的每一个人都要经过架设在火狱上面的桥，这是真主的判决，谁也不能阻挡祂的判决。</p>"
        },
        "72": {
            "verses": {
                "19:72": {
                    "id": 72
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>然后，我要拯救那些服从主的命令，远离主的禁令的敬畏者，我要让不义者跪在火狱里，他们无法逃出。</p>"
        },
        "73": {
            "verses": {
                "19:73": {
                    "id": 73
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当有人宣读我降示给使者的迹象时，否认者对信士说：“哪一伙人地位更优越，会场更优美呢？是我们，还是你们？”</p>"
        },
        "74": {
            "verses": {
                "19:74": {
                    "id": 74
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在他们之前，我曾毁灭了许多民族，那些民族比他们财产更多，物质方面更丰富。</p>"
        },
        "75": {
            "verses": {
                "19:75": {
                    "id": 75
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你说：“谁在迷误之中，愿真主优容他，使他更迷误，直到当他们目睹曾经在今世被警告的刑罚。”那时，他们将会知道谁的地位更恶劣，谁的军队更懦弱。是他们呢？还是信士们？</p>"
        },
        "76": {
            "verses": {
                "19:76": {
                    "id": 76
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>与此同时，真主要增加那些遵循正道者的信仰和善功。使者啊！在你的主看来，能使人获得永恒幸福的善功才是报酬更好，结局更善的。</p>"
        },
        "77": {
            "verses": {
                "19:77": {
                    "id": 77
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你告诉我吧。有人否认我的证据和警告。他说：“如果我死了，然后被复活，我必定要被赐予大量的财产和子女。”</p>"
        },
        "78": {
            "verses": {
                "19:78": {
                    "id": 78
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道他知道幽玄吗？他说的话有证据吗？还是他与真主订约，真主必使他进入乐园，必定赏赐他大量的财产和子女？</p>"
        },
        "79": {
            "verses": {
                "19:79": {
                    "id": 79
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>事情并非如他所称，我将记录他的所言所行，并由于他的谬论而加倍地惩罚他。</p>"
        },
        "80": {
            "verses": {
                "19:80": {
                    "id": 80
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我将继承他留下的财产和子女。在复活日，他将孤独地来见我。他曾享有的财产和地位都被剥夺了。</p>"
        },
        "81": {
            "verses": {
                "19:81": {
                    "id": 81
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以物配主的人舍真主而崇拜许多神灵，以便那些神灵援助他们。</p>"
        },
        "82": {
            "verses": {
                "19:82": {
                    "id": 82
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>事情并非他们所称的那样。在复活日，他们舍真主而崇拜的神灵将否认他们的崇拜，与他们断绝关系，并成为他们的敌人。</p>"
        },
        "83": {
            "verses": {
                "19:83": {
                    "id": 83
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！难道你没有看见，我派遣恶魔，让他们诱惑否认者犯罪，并对他们阻挡真主的宗教吗？</p>"
        },
        "84": {
            "verses": {
                "19:84": {
                    "id": 84
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你不要急于要求真主毁灭他们。我只计算他们的寿数，当宽限的日期结束时，我必使他们遭受应得的惩罚。</p>"
        },
        "85": {
            "verses": {
                "19:85": {
                    "id": 85
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当提及复活日。那时，我要使敬畏者——服从主命，远离禁令的人——受优待地回到他们的主那里。</p>"
        },
        "86": {
            "verses": {
                "19:86": {
                    "id": 86
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我要驱赶饥渴的否认者进火狱。</p>"
        },
        "87": {
            "verses": {
                "19:87": {
                    "id": 87
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这些否认者无法为彼此说情，除非是在今世以信仰真主和使者而与主订约的人。</p>"
        },
        "88": {
            "verses": {
                "19:88": {
                    "id": 88
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>犹太教徒和基督教徒及部分以物配主者说：“至仁主收养了儿子。”</p>"
        },
        "89": {
            "verses": {
                "19:89": {
                    "id": 89
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这样说的人确已犯了一件大罪。</p>"
        },
        "90": {
            "verses": {
                "19:90": {
                    "id": 90
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>为了这一谬论，天几乎要破，地几乎要裂，山几乎要崩。</p>"
        },
        "91": {
            "verses": {
                "19:91": {
                    "id": 91
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这是因为他们妄称至仁主有儿子，真主的大能远远地超越此事。</p>"
        },
        "92": {
            "verses": {
                "19:92": {
                    "id": 92
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>至仁主不会收养儿子，祂是纯洁无染的。</p>"
        },
        "93": {
            "verses": {
                "19:93": {
                    "id": 93
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>天地间的天使、人类和精灵，在复活日都将谦恭地见主。</p>"
        },
        "94": {
            "verses": {
                "19:94": {
                    "id": 94
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主全知他们，统计过他们的数目，他们的任何事都瞒不过真主。</p>"
        },
        "95": {
            "verses": {
                "19:95": {
                    "id": 95
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在复活日，每个人都要孤独地来见主，没有援助者，也没有财产。</p>"
        },
        "96": {
            "verses": {
                "19:96": {
                    "id": 96
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>信道并行善者，真主将使他们获得祂的喜爱，并获得人们的喜爱。</p>"
        },
        "97": {
            "verses": {
                "19:97": {
                    "id": 97
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！我以你的语言降示《古兰经》，使其成为容易的，以便你以此向服从我的命令，远离我的禁令的敬畏者报喜，并以此警告顽固不化、反对真理的否认者。</p>"
        },
        "98": {
            "verses": {
                "19:98": {
                    "id": 98
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在你的族人之前，我曾毁灭了许多民族。你是否发现了那些民族中的任何人，或听到他们发出的微声？当真主意欲的时候，他们所遭到的惩罚也许会降临到其他民族的身上。</p>"
        }
    }
}